Details: Avanti is an award winning social enterprise established by IIT alumni in 2010 to provide an affordable, high-quality education to disadvantaged students aspiring to study at Indias top colleges. At present, we have 80 full-time employees and 300 volunteersand support over 1,200 high school students in 12 locations across India.Avantis work is helping create a dramatic shift in how students learn Math and Science. We implement a pedagogy called Peer Instruction that reduces teacher dependence and enables collaborative learning. Students consume lecture content in the form of recorded videos and reading the material before attending class. In place of conventional lectures, classroom time is used to get students to work collaboratively on problem sets and clarify doubts by interacting with subject experts. Over the past two years, we have shown that our students outperform the most expensive after-school programs in the country at less than one-fourth the cost.Avanti is a PanIIT Alumni initiative, winner of Stanford BASES 2010 and recipient of the Echoing Green, Ashoka and Draper Richards Kaplan Fellowships for our work in reducing education inequity. Our co-founder was nominated to the Forbes 2014 List of 30 under 30 social entrepreneurs. Our last investment round was led by the Pearson Affordable Learning Fund. Our academic board is chaired by Prof. Eric Mazur, Dean of Applied Physics at Harvard University and world-renowned expert in Peer Instruction.

Details: World Wide Education is an overseas educational consultants organization based at Bhopal, dedicated towards providing education consultancy services to Indian students regarding higher education in various countries such as UK, USA, Canada, Australia, New Zealand, Singapore, Ireland, France, Malaysia. World Wide Education provides a wide array of services and resources, right from basic information on overseas education to the entire admission and visa process, including in-depth details about the Universities. We area solution-oriented company, having expertise in paving career paths for the students, to suit individual profiles within the prevailing parameters that may be educational, financial or personal.With a vision and mission to train and prepare our students to emerge as an ideal applicant, acceptable by all institutions, we strive to serve as a launching pad to an individuals professional career. We believe in Professionalism, Performance and are committed to deliver our best services to our students. We are committed to the highest standards of education excellence and quality of services.Some of our counselors have worked and studied abroad. Our excellent network with the Universities helps the student to choose the best university suitable to his requirements. World Wide Education dispels all the myths usually associated with "Overseas Education" and has brought the concept of 'Study Abroad' within the reach of every student, by making it affordable and devoid of cumbersome procedures.
